stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Active: Create and confirm schedule
    Active --> Paused: Pause
    Paused --> Active: Resume
    Active --> Completed: Course completed
    Paused --> Completed: Mark completed
    Active --> Stopped: Stop medicine
    Paused --> Stopped: Stop medicine
    Completed --> [*]
    Stopped --> [*]

    note right of Active
      Generates future reminder instances
      Tracks stock and low-stock threshold
    end note

    note right of Paused
      Future reminders are suspended
      History remains visible
    end note
